Package org.apache.pivot.collections

Class LinkedList<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.pivot.collections.LinkedList<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - The type of object stored in the list.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Iterable<T>, Collection<T>, List<T>, Sequence<T>
    public class LinkedList<T>
extends java.lang.Object
implements List<T>, java.io.Serializable
    Implementation of the List interface that is backed by a linked list.

    NOTE This class is not thread-safe. For concurrent access, use a SynchronizedList.
